title: [Rack 'Em Up, Slaughter Room]
description: Two wooden tables create an "L" shape in the northeastern corner of the room.  The surfaces seeped in a viscous, black ichor that emits a putrid stench in the air.  Half-taxidermied animals are strewn across the room, their pelts molding away in patches that expose the skeletal frame beneath.  A large statue of a grizzly bear standing on its hind legs stands eight feet tall near the table with a claw holding onto a basket.
